Title: With All Those Other Dogs Howling
Description: April 31
Commentary: A Hafiz-Emerson-Ladinsky bonus poem, just in case there ever is
  an ... April31.
---
Once I was asked, “Hafiz, why do you write poetry?”

To which I quickly responded,

“With all those other dogs howling, I thought I might as well

join

in!”
